    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the resistance thing but it just feels like my body is wrestling with chemicals it doesn't need anymore since the wound is closed and there's no pain. isn't the whole point of the medicine to kill the bacteria, and if they're all dead, doesn't the medicine just become a burden on my liver and gut? like, if the symptoms are 100% gone, is there actually any clinical reason to keep taking them?",
